![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3484bb3a-f7a7-4442-b480-dc4ca3b7ebda/20240529_170508.jpg?format=original)

Mercedes Mone opens the show celebrating her TBS title win. She asks the crowd was she worth the wait. She was, in fact, worth the wait.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/54978a70-07e2-4769-8f1e-480634dd2841/20240529_170605.jpg?format=original)

Skye Blue appears on video and reveals she is the one who attacked Mercedes Mone 3 weeks ago backstage. She wants the TBS title.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d1ef850f-cee5-41d8-9477-a5dfd8d09f38/Screenshot_20240529_173333.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_SWERVE STRICKLAND DEF. KILLSWITCH/LUCHASAURUS_**
    

Pretty fun match. Swerve finally gets revenge and takes some hair from Luchasaurus after having gotten some taken from him.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/dd0512b5-8ce1-45b2-b45f-fe3b53d1a747/20240529_173542.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ed00cc4e-544e-4f8b-9e9b-66ec230271f1/20240529_173606.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_TV TIME WITH THE LEARNING TREE CHRIS JERICHO_**
    

SO. MANY. TREE PUNS.

Chris Jericho and Big Bill invite Bryan Keith out to join them. Keith says he is tired of the way people talk about and treat Jericho.

Hook is out to fight all three of them when he’s interrupted by Samoa Joe. Joe whispers something into Hooks ear.

Joe and Hook leave together

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/97ac4bac-2634-4c07-acb7-cb8b0cc9aadb/20240529_173855.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/bb000882-d87e-466e-bf0c-015ea25c5222/Screenshot_20240529_174335.jpg?format=original)

NJPW Strong Womens Champion, CMLL's Stephanie Vaquer is set to debut in AEW on the Road to Forbidden Door.

A promo video airs tells us who she is and what she's done around the world.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c6313df3-b4c5-4d8e-9d64-65c77f1b8bb9/Screenshot_20240529_174654.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_IWGP HEAVYWEIGHT CHAMPIONSHIP ELIMINATOR MATCH: JON MOXLEY DEF. ROCKY ROMERO_**
    

Fun match. Moxley still selling the arm from this past weekend.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ed34a235-84c1-458c-a09f-b26451303284/20240529_175410.jpg?format=original)

Samoa Joe and Hook appear to be a new team going forward

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/96e31c76-6bf9-4c0a-be10-2c5101e95ecd/20240529_180022.jpg?format=original)

Don Callis is out to offer Orange Cassidy a contract. He's drowned out by the crowd but Orange comes out before Callis can finish speaking.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/24431327-4e05-4402-85b0-31e07699f749/20240529_180041.jpg?format=original)

Orange Cassidy takes Don Callis contract. Slowly rips it up. He tells Callis no. Then Stokely Hathaway and Kris Statlander come out.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c63da420-1350-4cde-8bd4-bdeca250b4c0/20240529_180418.jpg?format=original)

Kris says on behalf of her best friend, he accepts the invitation into the Family. Trent is revealed to be the newest member of the Don Callis Family.

Trent beats OC bloody and hugs Don Callis the way the Best Friends used to.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1a525d35-060d-4800-b241-2d7e6aee66b9/Screenshot_20240529_180441.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e34fe97b-d65b-49f1-9b7b-72115da8074f/20240529_181853.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_TBS CHAMPIONSHIP: MERCEDES MONE(c) DEF. SKYE BLUE_**
    

Great match but that finisher of Mercedes is still quite awkward.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f909c908-62d8-41a4-afd5-2c729d1480e6/20240529_181757.jpg?format=original)

Afterward, Stephanie Vaquer comes out and seems to challenge Mercedes to a rematch from their previous encounter.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/86cd02aa-0693-4ea1-96b1-21099e0a39fa/20240529_183354.jpg?format=original)

The Elite are out to strip Adam Copeland of the TNT Championship and to award it to Jack Perry.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e7e801a6-c103-483f-8e59-cb90ef0b8cb8/20240529_183426.jpg?format=original)

Jack Perry is mid celebration when Christopher Daniels returns to AEW and is named interim EVP. Daniels will be making announcements directly for Tony Khan from now on.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/98d80799-e0e7-4647-bb3b-dceeeb00fe0e/20240529_183419.jpg?format=original)

The TNT Championship will be decided in a Ladder match at Forbidden Door. Qualifying matches will be held over the next few weeks.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7aa98cd5-5a05-4f00-b114-749d531ca63e/20240529_184835.jpg?format=original)

